commit.message:
feat(sse): Phase 7C — handle SessionFaulted, WarmupCompleted, FileReloaded, SystemAlarm

- sse.lua: classify SessionFaulted/WarmupCompleted/FileReloaded/SystemAlarm (PascalCase + snake_case)
- events.lua: add SageFsSessionFaulted/WarmupCompleted/FileReloaded/SystemAlarm to EVENT_NAMES + EVENT_MAP
- init.lua: 4 new SSE handlers with correct UX contract:
  * session_faulted: ERROR notify + clear testing/coverage state + autocmd {session_id, reason}
  * warmup_completed: INFO notify (opt-out via notify_warmup_completed=false) + autocmd {session_id, project_count}
  * file_reloaded: silent state update (M.last_reload_file/ms) + autocmd {file, elapsed_ms}
  * system_alarm: ERROR notify (phase+message) + M.system_alarm for statusline + autocmd {phase, message}
- init.lua: M.system_alarm/last_reload_file/last_reload_ms state added
- init.lua: statusline shows [⚠ ALARM [phase]] when M.system_alarm is set
- spec: 12 new sse_spec tests + 10 new events_spec tests — 1160 successes / 0 failures

